{
  "stem": "942.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And once the pit was full, it was covered with a lot of straw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then dirt was put on top, so it will not freeze during the winter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was in an afternoon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we heard a siren from Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This was outside Birkenau, about two kilometers from Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we heard a siren from Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And usually the sound of a siren meant that there was an escape.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One siren, one blow of the siren-- and that meant to warn the guards on the towers all around, you know, the three-- it was called a [GERMAN], the post chain.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Post [GERMAN] is a chain, and post is the tower.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were three [GERMAN] to warn them to be on their toes, because there is an escape.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we could hear shooting and yelling and dogs barking, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this sound was coming closer to where we were working.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And you know, we didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But then we started to see some, you know, small, you know, dots running.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the sound was getting bigger in volume.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this Sergeant Kunz-- we were about 150 or so people in this group-- and he ordered us immediately to lay down on the ground face down.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had about 30 guards with us, approximately, with sub-machine guns or, or regular guns and dogs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he left two guards guarding us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he told them that if anybody lifts their head, to shoot them immediately.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he took the rest of the guards with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was-- not far from us, there was a pasture.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And there were horses in this pasture.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
